，而竊佔他人之不動產者，依前\r\n項之規定處斷。\r\n前二項之未遂犯罰之。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CHDM/111%2c%e7%b0%a1%2c221%2c20220217%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CHDM,111,簡,221,20220217,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"簡","JNO":"221","JDATE":"20220217","JTITLE":"竊盜"}